{"tid":1465090,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"還原基本步 回想一開始機埸和你飛係點","createTime":"2019-08-13T15:47:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T16:06:18.000Z","uid":178887,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"34014f1cd429a4649cf748cd05b52e8bcaa117f7","tid":1465090,"uid":178887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:47:27.000Z","msg":"機埸本來就唔係勇武嘅地方 我知大家好嬲好憤怒 但係一定要保持冷靜同理性思考<br />\n<br />\n我唔會話邊個岩邊個錯 不分化不割席<br />\n純粹個人睇法<br />\n<br />\n我地點解唔回想返初初和你飛係點？<br />\n其實好簡單 大家去機埸集會 俾全世界知香港發生緊咩事 用人數塞爆佢 唔好主動阻礙旅客<br />\n日日塞 好似812咁和理非一樣逼到佢停飛<br />\n<br />\n我覺得大家好似太急躁 好似想幾日分到勝負咁<br />\n又想100%完全停曬 停唔曬都好似輸左咁<br />\n希望大家記住呢個係長期戰 <br />\n日日塞 日日停啲都夠林奠死"},{"pid":"f1963cd196b2bf8005ddee01fa8fdc685cd8b072","tid":1465090,"uid":178887,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:48:01.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"f769ee5aaf2e404d5ce31fcc23995df08b15b81b","tid":1465090,"uid":178887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:50:48.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"5523fbe586729b85456b285e09c043cc5782ed4b","tid":1465090,"uid":178887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:51:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"283cc7a18ed6e015e79c4a68d956a1a772621c1c","tid":1465090,"uid":178887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:57:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d30c9b64dcad418ab429edf4f89bffc0abf08bc1","tid":1465090,"uid":178887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:57:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d898b2ded105b569f69138034efe96e8dfb42d58","tid":1465090,"uid":178887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:06:18.000Z","msg":"推"}]}